doctype html
html
    head
        include includes/header.pug
        title #{appName} | About
    body
        .mj-header.text-center
            span.mj-header-background
            .container
                h1.mj-header-title About
        .container
            p.lead MovieJazz will help you find the lowest prices on movies, at a range of different theatres
            p This application was developed in 2 weeks, collating data from two separate providers, which exposed a RESTful API.
            p
                | This application was required to run smoothly, without too much delay,
                | even when the providers fell over. With some caching magic,
                | we achieved a great middle ground, showing live data when possible,
                | and resorting to cache when the providers fail.
            p
                | Please contact me at #[a(href='mailto:georgewpaton@me.com') georgewpaton@me.com]
                | if what you see here is of interest to you, or your company
            p Have a great day!
        
        include includes/footer.pug